TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_PERIOD.SHORTNAME as PERIODSHORTNAME, CS_PERIOD.STARTDATE as PERIODSTARTDATE, CS_PERIOD.ENDDATE as PERIODENDDATE, CS_PERIOD.NAME AS PERIODNAME FROM CS_PERIOD@TC_LINK CS_PERIOD,CS_PERIODTYPE@TC_LINK CS_PERIODTYPE,CS_CALENDAR@TC_LINK WHERE CS_CALENDAR.NAME= '$$STR_CALENDAR_NAME' AND CS_PERIODTYPE.NAME = '$$STR_PERIOD_TYPE'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: AIASG_DPI_RPT_TABLE_MH.PERIODNAME IN (SELECT TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM $$TC_DB_SCHEMA_NAME.OUT_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='DPI_PERIOD_NAME' )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL'
